      "raw_text": "This taken late in the fall after the grass had\nbeen cut, but it gives you idea of the beautiful\ncountry have here Immediately in front Of you is\nbeautiful timothy meadow where the writer has\nit grow as high as his head The little white spot to\nthe right of the picture at the base of the hill is Mt\nHebron. You can see several of the buildings there.\nAll the country between your position in the picture\nand the town is beautiful producing country all under\nirrigation fine meadows and grain fields and mag\nnificent crops."
